cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DL, cs.SI 

The paper proposes a novel recommendation solution based on a marriage of deep reinforcement learning and knowledge distillation techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning techniques, which makes cs.DL (Deep Learning) a likely sub-category as well. Finally, the paper discusses the collaboration with Samsung Game Launcher, which suggests that cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) could also be a possible sub-category.
